            <h2>Meet Max</h2>
            <h4>Born February 2001</h4>
            <p>Max is a respectful, energetic young man who is looking to be a part of a fun and active family. He enjoys going to the park and playing any kind of game that is available. Max enjoys playing mid-field in soccer but also likes to watch football and basketball on TV.</p>
<p>Aside from playing sports and being outside, Max likes to play video games. His favorite games are Call of Duty 2 and 3. Max enjoys listening to rap music as well. His favorite artists are Migos and Kevin Gates. When it comes to food, Max loves chicken wings.</p>
<p>School is really important to Max as well. His favorite class is science and would like to become an Entrepreneur one day.</p>

